descriptionHtml:
This mod is for busy people, and/or mod reviewers who don\'t have time to level up their characters in the traditional way.

Find the Cheat Chest in Tamriel between Helgen and the Standing Stones on your map.

Recommended order of operation:

1. Add Skill Points
2. Add Perk Points
3. Add Combat Group
4. Add Magic Group
5. Add Stealth Group
6. Add Crafting Ingredients
7. Add Crafting Supplies

Does not require any DLCs or Script Extenders.
Tested. Works.
author: ordersomething
